# API Configuration
# Set this to your backend API base URL (include scheme and trailing /api)
# Example for local development:
# REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api
# Example for Render production (set this in Render dashboard env vars):
# REACT_APP_API_URL=https://lms-backend.onrender.com/api
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api

# NOTE: Create-react-app inlines REACT_APP_* variables at build time.
# If you change this variable in your hosting platform, you must rebuild/redeploy the frontend
# for the new value to be embedded into the static assets.
